text: Motion
Motion
Mmm~...

What's wrong, Hinana?
You're groaning so much.

Aha~
Was Hinana groaning~?

Yeah, you were.
What's up? If you have any worries...

Not at all~
Take a look at this~?

Hmm...?
This is... a delicious-looking cream puff, isn't it?

Right~?
The toppings are luxurious, and it looks so tasty~...

Mmm... So, this is a limited edition,
and even though they're selling it near the office...

It's just that because of the training camp,
Hinana can't go buy it~...

Oh, I see.
That's too bad...

Aha~
Producer, seeing the picture, do you want to eat it too~?

Haha, yeah,
it looks really delicious.

That's right~
Well, it can't be helped, right~?

Um...
I wish there was a way to get it somehow.

Oh~, Producer, did seeing the picture
make you want to eat it that badly~?

Eh... No,
not me, it's just────...

But, it can't be helped.
It's the training camp, so we have to endure, right~?

Haha... Yeah, that's right.
Hinana's right about that...!
